Dialogue: 0,0:01:41.26,0:01:43.80,Nadpis,,0,0,0,, 4\NVražda u dvora
Dialogue: 0,0:02:10.06,0:02:12.73,Nadpis,,0,0,0,,Taira no Kijomori\NMACUJAMA Ken'iči
Dialogue: 0,0:02:14.76,0:02:17.46,Nadpis,,0,0,0,,Minamoto no Jošimoto\NTAMAKI Hiroši
Dialogue: 0,0:02:23.37,0:02:25.64,Nadpis,,0,0,0,,Císař Toba\NMIKAMI Hiroši
Dialogue: 0,0:02:26.87,0:02:29.51,Nadpis,,0,0,0,,Taira no Tadamasa\NTOJOHARA Kosuke
Dialogue: 0,0:03:32.37,0:03:35.08,Nadpis,,0,0,0,,Fudžiwara no Tadazane\NKUNIMURA Džun
Dialogue: 0,0:03:38.68,0:03:41.11,Nadpis,,0,0,0,,Taira no Tadamori\NNAKAI Kiiči
